  "body": "Did you ever want to **listen** to the **Lava Chicken Music** from the \"**A Minecraft Movie**\" **in-game?**\n\nWell **now you can!**\nThis Resourcepack **replaces the \"Lava Chicken\" music disc with the \"Lava Chicken\" Song from the \"A Minecraft Movie!\"**\n\n## ℹ️ This pack has 2 variants:\n### 1. Extended Version:\n<iframe width=\"1396\" height=\"785\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/SILUNtF7lrs\" title=\"A Minecraft Movie Soundtrack | Steve’s Lava Chicken (Extended Version - Lyric Video) - Jack Black\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n### 2. Normal (Movie) Version:\n<iframe width=\"1396\" height=\"785\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/41O_MydqxTU\" title=\"Jack Black - Steve&#39;s Lava Chicken (Official Music Video) | A Minecraft Movie Soundtrack | WaterTower\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n<small>This is <b>NOT</b> a demonstration of this resourcepack and is only linked for fun:</small><iframe width=\"1236\" height=\"695\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/QA4rUwrRXyM\" title=\"I made Chickens dance to 🎶 Lava Chicken in Minecraft\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen></iframe>\n\n### **All rights go to: Mojang Studios, Warner Brothers, WaterTower Music**\n\nSang by: **Jack Black**",
